name: -Stat Growth/Setup Example-
note:
Stats need to be kept within 200 points for
first level, tied between Luck, Agility, 
Defense, Attack, Magic Attack and 
Magic Defense. HP counts as 10 per point and
MP is 3 per point.
Must have 1 Fast, 1 Kinda Fast, 4 normal,
1 kinda slow, and 1 slow.

name: Wraithborn Avenger
note:
This class has Moderate HP, MP, 
Agility and Luck growth, 
Great P. Attack, P. Defense, M. Attack and
M. Defense growth.

name: Moltentouched Sentinel
note:
This class has Great P. Defense growth,
Good HP growth, Moderate P. Attack,
M. Attack, M. Defense and Luck growth,
Low MP growth and Terrible Agility growth.

name: Frostflow Warden
